Comment: A nice problem for Clash of Code. Fast solutions possible - tests the competitors' ability to understanding the description quickly and implement a short solution.

My solution:
```
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

using namespace std;

int main() {
    string s;
    cin >> s;
    int sum = 0;
    for (char c : s) {
        if ('0' <= c && c <= '9') sum += c-'0';
        else sum += c-'A'+10;
    }
    cout << sum << endl;
}
```
